>\n但係完全唔覺得攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得小朋友係絕對可以練到跑到10k<br />\n至於要跑到呢個成績<br />\n真係要個老豆識練同日子有功"},{"pid":"986da0a57dfd932ef9f79dde8a74a03f4332c736","tid":892073,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T18:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}